com.dhemery.expressions.diagnosing

Class NamedPredicate<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dhemery.expressions.diagnosing.DescribedByName
      • com.dhemery.expressions.diagnosing.NamedPredicate<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the input to the predicate
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    SelfDescribingPredicate<T>, Predicate<T>, SelfDescribing

    public class NamedPredicate<T>
extends DescribedByName
implements SelfDescribingPredicate<T>
    A Predicate that describes itself by name. Each composed predicate created by this predicate is named to describe the composition.
